    <item>
      <title>加纳将与债券持有人启动债务重组谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/ghana-to-start-debt-restructuring-negotiations-with-bondholders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，加纳当局和国际债券持有人预计将于本周开始谈判，旨在达成一项重组约 130 亿美元违约全球债务的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/ghana-to-start-debt-restructuring-negotiations-with-bondholders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:20:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马拉松首席执行官预测，随着银行撤退，资产抵押贷款将蓬勃发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/marathon-ceo-bruce-richards-predicts-asset-based-lending-boom-as-banks-retreat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马拉松资产管理公司首席执行官兼董事长布鲁斯·理查兹表示，音乐版税和飞机等资产支持的贷款市场正在呈指数级增长，规模预计将超过 1 万亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/marathon-ceo-bruce-richards-predicts-asset-based-lending-boom-as-banks-retreat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:18:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Adobe 预计 AI 竞争加剧，销售额低迷</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/adobe-projects-lackluster-sales-with-ai-competition-intensifying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Adobe Inc. 对本季度的销售前景表示疲弱，引发了人们对新的专注于人工智能的初创公司构成竞争威胁的担忧。该股在盘后交易中下跌约 9%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/adobe-projects-lackluster-sales-with-ai-competition-intensifying</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法官称 Byju’s 必须冻结贷方赢得的 5.33 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/judge-says-byju-s-must-freeze-533-million-in-win-for-lenders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度科技公司 Think &amp;美国法官周四表示，Learn Pvt 必须冻结 5.33 亿美元，以保护心怀不满的贷方的资金，这些贷方声称现金只能用于支付他们的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/judge-says-byju-s-must-freeze-533-million-in-win-for-lenders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:12:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯托纳拉斯称欧洲央行已实现欧元区软着陆</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/ecb-has-achieved-soft-landing-for-euro-zone-stournaras-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊央行行长雅尼斯·斯图尔纳拉斯 (Yannis Stournaras) 于 2016 年 11 月 25 日星期五在希腊雅典的银行总部接受采访时发表讲话。斯图尔纳拉斯表示，现在谈论逐步结束欧洲央行债券购买计划“还为时过早”说。摄影师：Yorgos Karahalis /彭博社]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/ecb-has-achieved-soft-landing-for-euro-zone-stournaras-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 20:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>第一种治疗常见致命性肝病的药物获得美国批准</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/first-drug-to-treat-common-lethal-liver-disease-gets-us-nod</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Madrigal Pharmaceuticals Inc. 的药物 Rezdiffra 在美国首次获得批准，用于治疗一种可能致命的肝病，这种疾病影响了全球数百万人，在一些更大的竞争对手失败的领域取得了成功。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/first-drug-to-treat-common-lethal-liver-disease-gets-us-nod</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 19:53:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>克利夫斯在工会支持下对美国钢铁公司进行低价收购</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/cliffs-ceo-weighs-lowball-bid-for-us-steel-with-union-backing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cleveland-Cliffs Inc. 首席执行官 Lourenco Goncalves 表示，他将考虑另一次出价——在工会的支持下——美国钢铁公司的报价，尽管价格明显低于新日铁公司的现有报价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-14/cliffs-ceo-weighs-lowball-bid-for-us-steel-with-union-backing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 14 Mar 2024 19:27:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>通货膨胀抑制美联储押注，债券收益率飙升：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[另一份热门通胀报告强化了人们对美联储不会急于降息的押注，尽管某些经济领域显示出疲软迹象，但全球最大的债券市场遭到抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 22:32:47 GMT</pubDate>
